OL,4,G2225FPersonal Cinema: Maggie Smith
OL,5,     GIn a programme first broadcast in
OL,6,     G1970, Maggie Smith talks to
OL,7,     GMichael Aspel about her career
OL,8,     Gand chooses scenes from some of
OL,9,     Gher favourite films.
OL,10,G2255FTea with Mussolini
OL,11,     GItalian lad Luca, part-raised by
OL,12,     GEnglish ladies living in Florence
OL,13,     Gin 1935, re-enters their lives
OL,14,     Gjust as the encroaching war sees
OL,15,     Gthem forcibly relocated.
OL,16,G0045FHow to Get Ahead at Versailles
OL,17,     GStephen Smith explores the
OL,18,     GBaroque court of Louis XIV, who
OL,19,     Gcreated the Palace of Versailles
OL,20,     Gto surround himself with artists,
OL,21,     Gdesigners, gardeners, chefs and
OL,22,     Gmusicians.
